<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.112.24897.figure4>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Distribution map of Cremastosperma showing the four disjunct areas of the distribution: 1 the Choco / Darien / western Ecuador region north into Central America 2 the tropical Andes (including a rough demarcation between areas occupied by northern / lowland and southern / montane clades) 3 coastal Venezuela 4 French Guiana." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/245287" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

